deck: Enstranged wife of Kyle Barnes.
description:
Origin

Allison Barnes was married to Kyle Barnes and mother of Amber Barnes, when she was suddenly possessed by a demon. Kyle came home one day and saw her hurting their daughter, like his mother had hurt him all these years ago. Kyle drew the demon out of her after a violent struggle. When Allison regained consciousness, she saw the blood on herself and their daughter. Knowing the truth would sound crazy, Kyle took the blame on himself, telling Allison it was he who had attacked them. Allison took Amber and moved away from Kyle.

Major Story Arcs

A Vast and Unending Ruin

Allison has kept contact with Megan Holt to keep in touch with her enstranged husband Kyle.

Kyle visits her when he is in the neighborhood. Hiding behind a tree, he looks at Allison and their daughter Amber. Allison spots him and they have a heart-to-heart conversation. Not wanting to get back with Kyle, Allison calls Megan to pick Kyle up.

issue_credits.name: I Remember When She Loved Me

deck: Adopted sister of Kyle Barnes.
description:
Origin

After Kyle Barnes' mother was hospitalized, Kyle was placed in foster care with Megan's parents. Kyle was protective of Megan when he discovered she was molested by another foster boy named Donnie. Kyle slept on the floor of Megan's bedroom to stop Donnie. Instead of molesting Megan, Kyle took a beating everytime Donnie came by. Kyle was one of few kids that were actually adopted by Megan's parents. Now, married to Mark Holt, she looks after Kyle, who has become reclusive.

Origin

Sarah Barnes was possessed by a demon and terrorized her son, Kyle Barnes, throughout the years. One day, Kyle had enough of the torments and fought back. His touch hurt her and after a violent fight, the demon left her body. Finally free after years, Sarah went into a comatose state. Kyle Barnes was put into foster care, where he was adopted by the Holt family.

deck: Baptist reverend in West Virginia. He has done many exorcisms in his past.
description:
Origins

As a baptist reverend, Anderson has done many exorcisms in his past. Many of those, he still visits and cres for them with food packages, if they need it. When his area is again plagued by demon possessions, he sees Kyle Barnes (whom he had met when Kyle's mother was possessed) and asks him to go with him on his missions of exorcism. Together they try to discover the truth about the possessions and Kyle's role in them.

deck: Sidney is the leader of the demons that have possessed the residents of West Virginia.
description:
Origin

Not much is known about the enigmatic man known as Sidney, except that he seems to be the leader of the demons that plague the residents of West Virginia.

Major Story Arcs

A Darkness Surrounds Him

Sidney has come to West Virginia and visits a sermon held by Reverend Anderson. Shortly afterwards, he visits Sarah Barnes in the hospital.

To be close to Kyle Barnes, Sidney kills Kyle's neighbor Norville and takes residence in his home.

Sidney sents a warning to Reverend Anderson to stop his mission to discover the truth about the recent demon possessions. Sidney carves a pentagram in Anderson's chest.

description:
Origin

Donnie was placed in foster care with Megan's parents. Six months later, Kyle Barnes was placed in the same foster care. Kyle was protective of Megan when he discovered she was molested by Donnie. Kyle slept on the floor of Megan's bedroom to stop Donnie. Instead of molesting Megan, Kyle took a beating everytime Donnie came by.

Major Story Arcs

A Darkness Surrounds Him

Donnie claims to be a changed man and tries to make amends by apologizing to the people he hurt. However, he is not believed by them.
name: Donnie
